<item>
            <title>[LU-19856] remove ldiskfs patch series for rhel7.9 kernel</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19856</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The RHEL7.9 and earlier kernels are no longer supported.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Remove the &lt;tt&gt;ldiskfs-3.10-rhel7.9.series&lt;/tt&gt; file and all patches that are no longer used by this (or other) patch series.  The actual patches under &lt;tt&gt;ldiskfs/kernel_patches/patches/rhel7.x&lt;/tt&gt; may still be referenced by newer kernel series, so cannot be removed wholesale.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;./contrib/scripts/clearpatches.sh ldiskfs/kernel_patches&lt;/tt&gt; command will report which patches are no longer used by any series file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
